$gameVariables.setValue(21, "Br,ba,op.This radiator has seen better days. It’s covered in cobwebs and seems to be missing a part.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "Va,wo,cl.Brad. Have you seen Mendel? I can’t find him anywhere.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "Br,ba,ex.Buddie and Mendel already left to find a cell signal.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "Va,ba,op.What exactly did you two talk about earlier? You said Mendel is getting a helicopter. But why?");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "Va,sa,ex.Something you said changed his tune. What was it?");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "Br,wo,ex.Uh, well... Father Parker was drugging students just like Tillman was.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "Br,wo,op.Serum is in the water and Parker was extracting it.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "Va,wo,cl.Well... How do you know that there is Serum in the water here?");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "Br,wo,ex.Andy told me. I helped him escape the security room but made him spill the beans on Tillman.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "Va,wo,op.Oh my god. What did he tell you?");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "Br,sa,ex.Tillman and Andy were spiking the water supply. That’s why Tillman killed Denny. It’s not because of the porn video.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "Va,wo,cl.This goes so deep. I would have never guessed. ");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "Br,sa,op.Do you think ESU will get in trouble since Andy was making it there?");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "Va,sa,cl.Yes Dear. I think this spells disaster for us. ");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "Br,sa,op.Is there anything I can do to help?");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "Va,sa,op.It’s too late Brad. We just need to stay safe for now. When this is all over...");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "Va,sa,ex.No Dear. It’s okay. It’s time to move on.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "Va,sa,op.The only thing I care about right now is stopping Tillman and ending this.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "Va,fr,op.That’s Brave of you Dear. But it’s too dangerous.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "Va,sa,op.If something were to happen to you I’d never be able to live with myself.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "Br,sa,ex.And if I let something happen to you...");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "Br,fr,ex.I’ll never stop worrying about you. You’re my Brother’s Wife.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "Br,ba,op.I don’t care if it’s wrong. I want you.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "Br,ba,op.I’m not going to let anything happen to you. I will find Tillman and end this.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "Va,sa,op.I believe in you Dear. But I’m afraid. ");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "Br,fr,op.You don’t need to protect me Val. I can handle myself.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "Br,fl,ex.I’m already working on it. I’ll be safe Val. You can trust me.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "Va,sa,op.Don’t let anything happen to you baby. You’re the most important person to me now.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "Va,wo,ex.If Tillman finds you first... Play dumb. He doesn’t suspect you.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "Me,ba,ex.Brad. I couldn’t find her. Are you sure you saw Elizabeth in the east tower?");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "Br,wo,op.Oh well.. I mean she could be anywhere...");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "Br,fr,ex.She’s a crazy girl. I wouldn’t put it past her.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "Me,fr,op.Thanks Brad. Don’t worry. I’ll make sure I find her.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "Br,sa,op.Damn. He really wants to find her.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "Br,ba,op.Is he desperate to bury the evidence? Or does he really just want to protect the girls?");
